title: Houston beats 'Zona for Big 12 title, eyes 1 seed
description: Second-ranked Houston turned up its trademark defense in the final minute to hold on for a 72-64 victory over Arizona in the Big 12 Tournament championship game Saturday night.

title: Falcons keep Cousins, triggering bonus guarantee
description: The Falcons kept quarterback Kirk Cousins on their roster past 4 p.m. ET Saturday, triggering a guarantee on a $10 million roster bonus that is due in 2026.
author: Marc Raimondi

title: France overpower Scotland to win Six Nations title
description: France secured the Six Nations championship with a flourish - and quashed England's hopes - by ultimately overpowering a dogged Scotland in Paris.

title: 'Chelsea win round one but Man City retain belief'
description: One match down, three to go - and it was Chelsea who came out on top against Manchester City to win the League Cup in the first meeting of a quickfire four-game run.

title: McIlroy chases Spaun as wind causes chaos at Sawgrass

title: How prepared are Newcastle to end their 70-year wait for silverware?
description: I handed Eddie Howe a bottle of water before our cup final preview interview last week and he asked jokingly if the bottle had vodka in it.

title: Pete Alonso drives in run, Max Kranick allows first runs of spring in Mets' loss to Nationals
description: The Mets continued their spring training slate as they took on the Nationals on Saturday night, here's everything you need to know.

title: Golden State Warriors jersey history - No. 8 - Chris Washburn (1986-87)
description: During his time suiting up for the Warriors, Washburn wore only jersey No. 8 and put up 3.8 points, and 2.8 rebounds per game.
